room_title: Escape room "Nate's Motel" by Fantasy Escapes in Tampa
room_description: After driving for hours on end and starting to doze off at the wheel, you decide it’s a must to stop for the night. There’s nothing for miles in any direction until you stumble upon a quaint little motel and decide that this is your only option. As you walk inside, an immediate chill runs down your spine. After some deliberation, it seems like a good spot to lay your head, or is it?
